  "title": "CLOUD ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p>•Design, develop, and optimize SQLScript procedures in SAP HANA Cloud.</p><p>•Implement and maintain multi-container architecture (staging, target, procedures).</p><p>•Develop complex dynamic SQL and parameterized procedures.</p><p>•Enable parallel execution of procedures for performance optimization.</p><p>•Manage cross-container access using grants, synonyms, and roles.</p><p>•Perform table partitioning and SQL performance tuning.</p><p>•Support manual MTAR-based transport and environment synchronization.</p><p>•Collaborate with Datasphere and SAC teams to support reporting needs.</p><p>•Strong hands-on experience with SAP HANA Cloud SQLScript.</p><p>•Deep expertise in:</p><p>o Dynamic SQL</p><p>o Window functions</p><p>o Procedural programming</p><p>•Experience with multi-container HANA Cloud architecture.</p><p>•Familiarity with:</p><p>o JDBC-based data ingestion (e.g., Hadoop / non-SAP sources)</p><p>o SDA concepts (DP Agent, virtual tables – conceptual)</p><p>•Experience working in Business Application Studio (BAS).</p><p></p>",
